6:18:29 AM [express] GET /api/news/crypto 200 in 9422ms :: [{"id":"59093833","title":"Here's how traders and big buyers stepped in to keep bitcoin steady during the oil shock","summary":"Several market participants, including MSTR and OTC traders, kept demand steady, helping BTC stay resilient.","url":"https://www.coindesk.com/markets/2026/03/10/here-s-how-traders-and-big-buyers-stepped-in-to-keep-bitcoin-steady-during-the-oil-shock","source":"CoinDesk","publishedAt":"2026-03-10T06:14:24.000Z","imageUrl":"https://resources.cryptocompare.com/news/5/59093833.jpeg","sentiment":"Neutral","topics":["BTC","COMMODITY","MARKET","CRYPTOCURRENCY"]},{"id":"59093720","title":"Bhutan moves $11.8M in BTC from its national stash: Arkham","summary":"Bhutan has accumulated around 13,000 Bitcoin since launching state-backed mining operations in 2019, primarily fueled by hydroelectric energy.","url":"https://cointelegraph.com/news/bhutan-moves-11-8m-btc-from-national-stash-arkham?utm_source=rss_feed&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=rss_partner_inbound","source":"Cointelegraph","publishedAt":"2026-03-10T06:10:02.000Z","imageUrl":"https://images.cryptocompare.com/news/default/cointelegraph.png","sentiment":"Neutral","topics":["BTC","MINING","ARKM","CRYPTOCURRENCY"]},{"id":"59093719","title":"Vitalik Buterin envisions ‘one-click’ Ether staking for institutions","summary":"“We want the authority over staking nodes to be highly distributed, and the first step to doing this is to make it easy,” said Ethereum co-founder Vitalik Buterin.","url":"https://cointelegraph.com/news/vitalik-distributed-validator-technology-lite-simplify-institutional-eth-staking?utm_source=rss_feed&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=rss_partner_inbound","source":"Cointelegraph","publishedAt":"2026-03-10T06:06:56.000Z","imageUrl":"https://images.cryptocompare.com/news/default/cointelegraph.png","sentiment":"Neutral","topics":["ETH","CRYPTOCURRENCY"]},{"id":"59093513","title":"Crypto Funding Soars 50%, But Most Startups Are Getting Shut Out: Analysts","summary":"Three deals last February ate up nearly half of all the money raised in crypto that month. Just three. That single fact tells you more about where crypto funding stands right now than the headline numbers do. A Shrinking Pool Of Big Bets According to data from research firm Messari , total crypto fu","url":"https://bitcoinist.com/crypto-funding-soars-50-but-most-startups-are-getting-shut-out-analysts/","source":"Bitcoinist","publishedAt":"2026-03-10T06:00:55.000Z","imageUrl":"https://resources.cryptocompare.com/news/13/59093513.jpeg","sentiment":"Neutral","topics":["BTC","BUSINESS","EXCHANGE","MINING","CRYPTOCURRENCY"]},{"id":"59093468","title":"‘Bitcoin is going to die,’ says Oscar-nominated actor Terrence Howard","summary":"Is Bitcoin repeating its historical cycle pattern once again?","url":"https://ambcrypto.com/bitcoin-is-going-to-die-says-oscar-nominated-actor-terrence-howard/","source":"AMB Crypto","publishedAt":"2026-03-10T06:00:51.000Z","imageUrl":"https://images.cryptocompare.com/news/default/ambcrypto.png","sentiment":"Neutral","topics":["BTC","CRYPTOCURRENCY"]},{"id":"59093431","title":"Bitcoin’s Valuation Model Hints At $500K Cycle Average, Analyst Says","summary":"Bitcoin is trading near $67,300, well off its recent high of $74,000. One well-known analyst says that dip barely matters — he’s looking at a cycle average closer to half a million dollars. Related Reading: WAR Token Explodes 100%, Then Crashes 20% In Sudden Sell-Off A Model Built On Scarcity PlanB,","url":"https://www.newsbtc.com/bitcoin-news/bitcoins-valuation-model-hints-at-500k-cycle-average-analyst-says/","source":"NewsBTC","publishedAt":"2026-03-10T06:00:28.000Z","imageUrl":"https://resources.cryptocompare.com/news/21/59093431.jpeg","sentiment":"Neutral","topics":["BTC","BUSINESS","MARKET","TRADING","CRYPTOCURRENCY"]},{"id":"59093335","title":"Morning brief: Bitcoin gain; Asian stocks rally on Trump remarks","summary":"Global financial markets opened Tuesday with sharp swings across energy, equities, and cryptocurrencies as investors reacted to signals that the conflict involving Iran could be nearing an end. Oil prices plunged after US President Donald Trump suggested the war was nearly complete, easing fears of ","url":"https://invezz.com/news/2026/03/10/morning-brief-bitcoin-gain-asian-stocks-rally-on-trump-remarks/","source":"Invezz","publishedAt":"2026-03-10T05:56:50.000Z","imageUrl":"https://resources.cryptocompare.com/news/69/59093335.jpeg","sentiment":"Neutral","topics":["BTC","COMMODITY","MARKET","TRADING","CRYPTOCURRENCY"]},{"id":"59092815","title":"Bitcoin’s Leverage Ratio Drops Sharply – Is a Healthier Market Reset Underway?","summary":"Global tensions, particularly the Iran-US conflict, have rattled crypto markets and pushed investors away from risk-taking. “Periods like this are generally not favorable for risk-taking, and this can be clearly observed in the sharp decline of Bitcoin’s Estimated Leverage Ratio on Binance,” said Cr","url":"https://cryptopotato.com/bitcoins-leverage-ratio-drops-sharply-is-a-healthier-market-reset-underway/","source":"Crypto Potato","publishedAt":"2026-03-10T05:40:07.000Z","imageUrl":"https://resources.cryptocompare.com/news/27/59092815.jpeg","sentiment":"Neutral","topics":["BTC","MARKET","TRADING","BNB","CRYPTOCURRENCY"]}]
